WEBVTT

22:06.150 --> 22:08.240 line:80%
The front line is engulfed
in flames of war,

22:08.240 --> 22:10.480 line:80%
and our soldiers
are fighting bloody battles.

22:10.480 --> 22:12.740 line:80%
Provisions are the lifeline of the army.

22:12.800 --> 22:14.660 line:80%
